# .claude/ and .cursor/ are tracked (dogfood): the doccraft skills we
# ship are derivable from templates/, but OpenSpec's skills and slash
# commands (.claude/skills/openspec-*, .claude/commands/opsx/,
# .cursor/skills/openspec-*, .cursor/commands/opsx-*.md) are installed
# by `openspec init` from an external package and are not regenerable
# from this repo. Committing the whole dir keeps the in-repo agent
# environment reproducible without re-running install.
.claude/settings.local.json
